text: Pride of the Navy is a 1939 American action movie directed by Charles Lamont and starring James Dunn, Rochelle Hudson, Gordon Oliver, Horace McMahon, Charlotte Wynters, Charles Trowbridge. It was distributed by Republic Pictures. ==Other websites== * Category:1939 movies Category:1930s action movies Category:American action movies Category:Movies directed by Charles Lamont
